University Press, 1973.</li>

<li>Volney, C.F., 2010 [1802], <em>The Ruins</em>, Thomas Jefferson
(trans.), Fairford, England: The Echo Library.</li>

<li>Walton, C., 1984, &ldquo;Hume and Jefferson on the Uses of
