389&ndash;403.</li>

<li>Wiencek, H., 2012, &ldquo;Thomas Jefferson: Slave
Master,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>American History</em>, (October):
26&ndash;33.</li>

<li>Wilson, William, 2017, &ldquo;The Myth of Jefferson&rsquo;s
Deism,&rdquo; <em>The Elusive Thomas Jefferson: Essays on the Man
